info.description:
Utils module of `**pyLoad** <https://github.com/pyload/pyload>`_, *The
Free and Open Source download manager written in Pure Python and
designed to be extremely lightweight, fully customizable and remotely
manageable*.

    **Notice:** `Master
    Branch <https://github.com/pyload/utils/tree/master>`_ is under
    heavy development, very unstable, often broken. **Please, do not use
    it for now!**
